      • getDayEpochMs

        public static long getDayEpochMs​(int day)
        Turn day of week to epoch ms.

        1st of January 1970 (Epoch) is Thursday (-2).

        Parameters:
        day - 1 = Sunday, 2 = Monday etc.. 7 = Saturday
        Returns:
        Milliseconds since epoch for this day to be given by SimpleDateFormat "EEEE"
